cloud-output.log on VB,
{noformat}
2014-05-22 10:03:38  INFO | 10.111.5.145: BrokerReply {DescribeInstances:i-7078ef56/Extant(none/poweredOn), i-139e172f/Extant(none/poweredOn), i-a2fd6bb6/Extant(none/poweredOn), i-7022f5f5/Extant(none/poweredOn), i-16cd4803/Teardown(none/poweredOff), i-ab5ed5de/Extant(none/poweredOn), i-0f48112d/Pending(none/poweredOff), i-5d3b995e/Extant(none/poweredOn)}
